nsätze praxisbezogen. Zu jedem Kapitel gibt es umfassende Fallstudien, mit deren Hilfe ein Selbststudium möglich ist.   aThis volume presents the general principles and applications of mathematics and statistics in the financial industry. Work with case studies represents an additional focus of the book. It addresses the mathematical deficiencies experienced by so many students, and despite its mathematical orientation, is written clearly and comprehensibly.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jun 2020) 0aFinancexMathematical models. 0aFinancexStatistics. 4aCase study. 4aFallstudie. 4aFinanzen. 4aFinanzwirtschaft. 4aMathematik. 4aStatistik. 4aZinsrechnung. 4afinance. 4afinancial industry. 4ainterest calculation. 4amathematics. 4astatistics. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh1 aKalhöfer, Christian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2015z9783110438734oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831103985020 cprintz978348671648140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348672117140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486721171423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783486721171.jpg  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015